-- ZIP list FROM live communities (level='zip', state='NC' — 170 ZIPs);
-- centroids zipcodes PyPI v3.0.0, NC bbox-validated; 0 quarantined.
-- WIRED: wake-county-building-permits (arcgis, maps.wake.gov; 195,894 permits,
--   per-parcel geometry, spatial ZIP scope). Charlotte/Mecklenburg expose only
--   zoning-review polygons (no per-permit layer) -> facilities-floor.
-- GO-LIVE RESULT: see docs/source-registry.md "NORTH CAROLINA WIRE PASS".
